eld-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="44" data-field-top-res-375-value="64" data-field-left-res-375-value="23" data-field-height-res-375-value="114" data-field-width-res-375-value="328" data-field-fontsize-res-375-value="30" data-field-left-res-1200-value="35"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1702537037023'>Размещайте рекламу там, где её&nbsp;заметят</div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702481954616' data-elem-id='1702481954616' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="488" data-field-left-value="163" data-field-height-value="28" data-field-width-value="253" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="24" data-field-top-res-375-value="432" data-field-left-res-375-value="34" data-field-width-res-375-value="304" data-field-fontsize-res-375-value="20" data-field-top-res-1200-value="488" data-field-left-res-1200-value="47"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1702481954616'>Поисковый запрос</div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702480548658' data-elem-id='1702480548658' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="528" data-field-left-value="163" data-field-height-value="96" data-field-width-value="304" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="16" data-field-top-res-375-value="464" data-field-left-res-375-value="35" data-field-width-res-375-value="304" data-field-fontsize-res-375-value="14" data-field-top-res-1200-value="528" data-field-left-res-1200-value="47"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1702480548658'>Наши пользователи уже знают, какие товары и&nbsp;услуги им&nbsp;нужны. В&nbsp;2ГИС они найдут все компании, а&nbsp;с&nbsp;фильтрами смогут задать более точные критерии.</div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702537187749' data-elem-id='1702537187749' data-elem-type='image' data-field-top-value="221" data-field-left-value="144" data-field-height-value="247" data-field-width-value="352" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-filewidth-value="1056" data-field-fileheight-value="741" data-field-lazyoff-value="y" data-field-heightmode-value="hug" data-field-top-res-375-value="176" data-field-left-res-375-value="19" data-field-height-res-375-value="236" data-field-width-res-375-value="336" data-field-top-res-1200-value="221" data-field-left-res-1200-value="28" data-field-height-res-1200-value="247"> <div class='tn-atom'> <img class='tn-atom__img' src='https://static.tildacdn.com/tild3834-6538-4435-a265-333164333463/Image.png' alt='Поисковый запрос' imgfield='tn_img_1702537187749' /> </div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702537555912' data-elem-id='1702537555912' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="488" data-field-left-value="563" data-field-height-value="28" data-field-width-value="322" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="24" data-field-top-res-375-value="852" data-field-left-res-375-value="34" data-field-width-res-375-value="304" data-field-fontsize-res-375-value="20" data-field-top-res-1200-value="488" data-field-left-res-1200-value="443"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1702537555912'>Выбор компании</div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702537618144' data-elem-id='1702537618144' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="488" data-field-left-value="963" data-field-height-value="28" data-field-width-value="325" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="24" data-field-top-res-375-value="1272" data-field-left-res-375-value="34" data-field-width-res-375-value="304" data-field-fontsize-res-375-value="20" data-field-top-res-1200-value="488" data-field-left-res-1200-value="839"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1702537618144'>Покупка или заказ</div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702537618147' data-elem-id='1702537618147' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="528" data-field-left-value="963" data-field-height-value="96" data-field-width-value="304" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="16" data-field-top-res-375-value="1304" data-field-left-res-375-value="35" data-field-width-res-375-value="304" data-field-fontsize-res-375-value="14" data-field-top-res-1200-value="528" data-field-left-res-1200-value="839"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1702537618147'>Когда выбор сделан, 2ГИС поможет связаться с&nbsp;компанией: позвонить, перейти на&nbsp;сайт, оставить заявку или построить маршрут на&nbsp;любом транспорте или пешком.</div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702537555915' data-elem-id='1702537555915' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="528" data-field-left-value="563" data-field-height-value="96" data-field-width-value="304" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="16" data-field-top-res-375-value="884" data-field-left-res-375-value="35" data-field-width-res-375-value="304" data-field-fontsize-res-375-value="14" data-field-top-res-1200-value="528" data-field-left-res-1200-value="443"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1702537555915'>2ГИС выручает, когда нужно выбрать одно среди множества. В&nbsp;помощь пользователям&nbsp;— отзывы, фото, объявления о&nbsp;скидках и&nbsp;акциях. Всё это есть в&nbsp;карточке компании.</div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__19236982311702537618150' data-elem-id='1702537618150' data-elem-type='image' data-field-top-value="221" data-field-left-value="944" data-field-height-value="247" data-field-width-value="352" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-filewidth-value="704" data-field-fileheight-value="494" data-field-lazyoff-value="y" data-field-heightmode-value="hug" data-field-top-res-375-value="1016" data-field-left-res-375-value="19" data-field-height-res-375-value="236" data-field-width-res-375-value="336" data-field-top-res-1200-value="221" data-field-left-res-1200-value="820" data-field-height-res-1200-value="247"> <div class='tn-atom'> <img class='tn-atom__img' src='https://static.tildacdn.com/tild6634-3939-4832-b938-616563653463/Buy.png' alt='' imgfield='tn_img_1702537618150' /> </div> </div> <div class='t3